All exceptions defined by gedcom4j are found in this package.
infotrader.parser.io.encoding
Classes related to the encoding of data to/from internal string representations

Classes for supporting Observer pattern during I/O operations (which can be lengthy).

Classes related to reading data streams and files
infotrader.parser.io.writer

infotrader.parser.model
A data model for holding genealogical data.
infotrader.parser.parser
Classes for parsing GEDCOM-format data and constructing an object graph from it, using objects in the org.gedcom4j.model package.
infotrader.parser.parser.event
Classes for supporting Observer pattern during parse operations (which can be lengthy).
infotrader.parser.query
A package for classes that can help with common queries over the object model.
infotrader.parser.validate
Classes that can validate the data in the object model for a variety of problems, so that the data written by the Writer is compliant with the GEDCOM standard.
infotrader.parser.writer
Classes for writing GEDCOM files from the object model
infotrader.parser.writer.event
Classes for supporting Observer pattern during construction of string data for write operations (which can be lengthy).
